The quest "Restore Wolfsford's Reputation" is a new angle on the existing fact that Aldric Nightwhisper owes Cael Pendrake a debt of honor from an old quarrel over a stolen horse. Cael seeks to honor this debt by finding a way to restore Wolfsford's good name, without contradicting the earlier established fact. The quest offers a new narrative thread that aligns with the existing conflict, providing a unique opportunity for the player to interact with both Cael and Aldric while also addressing a historical conflict in the town.
